Since $\triangle BMP \sim \triangle BAP$, we have $\frac{BP}{AP}=\frac{BM}{AM}=\frac{20}{11}$. Thus, $\frac{CP}{PA}=\frac{BP-BC}{AP}=\frac{20}{11}-1=\frac{9}{11}$.

